<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="S. Stern" box="[1084,1227,1244,1265]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Solanaceae" genus="Solanum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="18" pageNumber="488" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="manabiense">
<emphasis box="[1084,1227,1244,1265]" italics="true" pageId="18" pageNumber="488">S. manabiense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
occurs (&lt;5,000 km 
<superScript attach="right" box="[1450,1459,1238,1252]" fontSize="6" pageId="18" pageNumber="488">2</superScript>
), the small number of known populations (&lt;5) and the few collections (4), it is given an IUCN Red List Status of Endangered.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
